vote.title: Authorize the City Manager to execute a contract for the disbursement of allocated Capital Construction Funds to Kitchen Dog Theater Company to be used for renovations to a newly purchased building through the Cultural Facilities Program - Not to exceed $112,998.50 - Financing: Capital Construction Fund
